Outlier treatment¶

In [17]:
# Rain
median = float(df["Rain (mm)"].median())
df["Rain (mm)"] = np.where(df["Rain (mm)"] >75, median,df['Rain (mm)'])
In [18]:
# Rain rate
median = float(df['Rain rate (mm/h)'].median())
df["Rain rate (mm/h)"] = np.where(df["Rain rate (mm/h)"] >75, median,df["Rain rate (mm/h)"])
